00:32:46.080 --> 00:32:49.840
The show is this weekend. and now the booth has decided to have no power.

566
00:32:49.920 --> 00:32:51.800
so I don't know what's going on with it.

567
00:32:53.160 --> 00:32:54.840
Isaac has mentioned this before.

568
00:32:54.920 --> 00:32:59.000
Hopefully. he can fix it. If not...  ...I don't know.

