00:33:03.960 --> 00:33:05.840
We can't get this booth running.

570
00:33:05.920 --> 00:33:08.600
It's as if there's no gas coming through at all. Right.

571
00:33:08.680 --> 00:33:12.400
Have you tried the little solenoid that way up on the far end? No.

572
00:33:17.320 --> 00:33:19.200
When the compressor has weird issues.

