00:33:19.280 --> 00:33:21.240
you just turn it on and off again. it works.

574
00:33:21.320 --> 00:33:24.840
So I don't think they've tried this yet. So. if I turn it off...

575
00:33:26.880 --> 00:33:30.120
Is it on now? Nothing at all. It's all gone.

576
00:33:31.040 --> 00:33:33.920
What about now? No. still nothing.

577
00:33:34.000 --> 00:33:36.920
All right. give me two seconds. I'll just have a go at this.

578
00:33:37.000 --> 00:33:39.200
Okay.

579
00:33:39.280 --> 00:33:41.400
What the hell is he doing up there?

580
00:33:42.840 --> 00:33:44.920
Jesus. Anything yet?

581
00:33:45.000 --> 00:33:46.600
There's nothing at all.

582
00:33:55.680 --> 00:33:58.360
Anything now? Yeah. it's on now.

583
00:33:58.440 --> 00:34:01.000
Right. Hopefully. now we should have some heat.

584
00:34:02.360 --> 00:34:05.000
Let's see if it's cutting in. Yeah. I can see flames.

585
00:34:05.080 --> 00:34:08.000
Yeah. it's fixed. Temperature's going up.

586
00:34:08.080 --> 00:34:10.880
What did you do? I just went in the...

587
00:34:10.960 --> 00:34:14.360
You know. the control panels. a few little switches. just reset them all.

