00:34:14.440 --> 00:34:16.920
Fair play to Isaac. he really helped us out there.

589
00:34:17.000 --> 00:34:19.800
I'm not sure what he did. but he's managed to get it going.

590
00:34:19.880 --> 00:34:22.160
At least it's running again. that's the main thing.

591
00:34:22.240 --> 00:34:24.280
We'll ignore the finer detail.

592
00:34:40.680 --> 00:34:43.920
So. F-100. So far. I've painted all the cream.

